Class CreateJoinTableRequest

    public class CreateJoinTableRequest
extends Object
implements org.apache.avro.generic.IndexedRecord
    A set of parameters for GPUdb.createJoinTable(CreateJoinTableRequest).

    Creates a joint_table which is a list of tables and aliases for those tables.

        Parameters:
        joinTableName - Name of the join_table to be created. Must not be the name of a currently existing GPUdb table or join_table. Cannot be an empty string.
        tableNames - The list of table names making up the joined set
        aliases - The list of aliases for each of the corresponding tables.
        options - Optional parameters.
